	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />ALso is there a way to change the command prompt Header (C:\Documents and Settings\(computername)&gt;) So that i dont have to put all my files in that folder, and i can have them in my own directories.  I think i can do it in 98 but im running and XP right now for the internet.

		

		</td>
